    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this simulation, you start by working in a small courier shop, delivering food orders around the city. Initially, you will take on simple orders, but over time, you will have the opportunity to grow your business. By completing deliveries on time, you can save up the money you earn and invest in faster and more efficient vehicles. Additionally, you can hire new employees to expand your company and increase your workforce. As you meet the city's transportation needs and grow your earnings, you will also have the chance to obtain different licenses, allowing you to expand your delivery business into various product categories. In the later stages of the game, you can strategically expand your trade network and service range to build a larger transportation empire.<br><br><br><br><br><br>   <strong>Game Content</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Delivery Missions:</strong> Complete deliveries on time to ensure customer satisfaction and earn income.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267870/extras/3b22f30c84c1a4b078974d400b865265.avif?t=1729795046\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267870/extras_big/3b22f30c84c1a4b078974d400b865265.avif?t=1729795046 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Vehicle Upgrades:</strong> Purchase new vehicles to increase your delivery capacity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267870/extras/b2f1ddce0048c3c33149b3e22cbd85c5.avif?t=1729795046\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267870/extras_big/b2f1ddce0048c3c33149b3e22cbd85c5.avif?t=1729795046 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Employee Management:</strong> Hire new employees to grow your company.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267870/extras/53e120d308712603e355aa54a1e09e93.avif?t=1729795046\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267870/extras_big/53e120d308712603e355aa54a1e09e93.avif?t=1729795046 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Licenses:</strong> Expand your delivery business by obtaining new product licenses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267870/extras/8c973e75deaeb9c882d72eecce4f819e.avif?t=1729795046\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267870/extras_big/8c973e75deaeb9c882d72eecce4f819e.avif?t=1729795046 width=800 height=800 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Strategic Growth:</strong> Use different strategies to establish the most profitable business model.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267870/extras/3a158ffc7f1e20e7c6a11119a5f7c4a7.avif?t=1729795046\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3267870/extras_big/3a158ffc7f1e20e7c6a11119a5f7c4a7.avif?t=1729795046 width=800 height=800 /></span></p></li></ul>",
